# S3 FUSE mount points (comma-separated, for direct filesystem access)
# If S3 is mounted via s3fs-fuse or similar, specify mount points here
# Example: DEPICTIO_S3_MOUNT_POINTS=/mnt/s3,/mnt/depictio-bucket
# DEPICTIO_S3_MOUNT_POINTS=/mnt/s3

